title: Fox Presents | The Search for Sasquatch
description:
The hunt for the mystical and elusive beast continues. Short commercial featuring Scotty Cranmer and Pat Casey. Our World Famous Sasquatch fur lined hoodies are often imitated but never duplicated.


Directed by:Ryan Marcus

Filmed by:Ryan Marcus and Veesh

Edited by:Veesh
